Package: mermaid2drawml
Type: Package
Title: Convert Mermaid Diagrams to Editable Word Shapes
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Author", "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "author@example.com")
Description: Converts Mermaid flowchart diagrams to natively editable Microsoft
    Word shapes using the DrawingML wps:wsp format. Layout and SVG rendering
    are delegated to the official Mermaid CLI (@mermaid-js/mermaid-cli), so
    Word output matches the HTML/browser rendering. The resulting shapes are
    editable in Word and can be inserted into documents via the officer package,
    suitable for use in R Markdown workflows. Run setup_mermaid2drawml() once
    after installation to download the required Node.js packages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: Node.js (>= 18), npm
